#Text=Tell us about the Vikeslandic culture .
#Text=Vikeslandic culture is an ever evolving thing .
#Text=We speak English and our lifestyles are a quintessential westerners life , but as more and more people become citizens they bring a variety of new things with them .
#Text=We heavily condone the arts in all forms and the majority of us love some part of the outdoors , be it camping , hiking or boating .
#Text=I am currently going to have an official Vikeslandic food recipe compilation made and posted on our website .
#Text=I hope to have authentic Vikeslandic food up there for everyone to try .
#Text=Being socially conscious and having a good time in this life is top of the list .
#Text=Does Vikesland belong to any international organizations ?
#Text=Yes , we currently belong to an intermicronational organization called The League of Small Nations .
#Text=It is an organization designed to advance the rights of small sovereign states and provide a platform from which their voices can be heard among the larger more powerful states .
#Text=Can one become a citizen of Vikesland ?
#Text=Is honorary citizenship granted ?
#Text=Yes , you can become a citizen of Vikesland by applying on our citizenship page .
#Text=We have two types of citizenry , cyber citizens ( honorary ) or full citizens .
#Text=Can people visit Vikesland ?
#Text=Yes they can but it is only by appointment .
#Text=Anyone showing up unannounced will be most likely turned away .
#Text=Requests can be made directly to myself via e-mail only .
#Text=What are your duties as prince ?
#Text=What is it like to run your own country ?
#Text=It is stressful being the head of state , it is a lot of fun but equally testing as well .
#Text=I oversee most government workings and provide leadership and direction for those under me .
#Text=I am also the face of Vikesland so I take care of all media related issues and some foreign diplomacy as well as keep the citizens informed via or website with video or write-ups .
#Text=I also head various projects within our security force and our Department of Aeronautics and Space .
#Text=It can be tough but it is equally rewarding .
#Text=There are thousands reading this right now .
#Text=Is there anything else you would like us to know about your nation ?
#Text=I would just like to reiterate that we are not secessionists or unpatriotic rebels of any-kind .
#Text=I personally am a very patriotic Canadian but I am also equally a patriotic Vikeslandic .
#Text=This nation project is a new frontier and immensely fun on top of it .
#Text=I consider myself a dual citizen of both Canada and Vikesland and I am law abiding .
#Text=It is with hope that one day we can achieve our own autonomy peacefully with our distinct culture and small land-base .
#Text=Semi-autonomy is even an acceptable outcome in the end .
#Text=The first and foremost of all of this is that everyone involved enjoy what they are doing .
#Text=I am not willing , nor am I asking anyone to ruin their health or professional life by relentlessly pursuing an impossible goal .
#Text=I believe that if it is not fun or beneficial , why do it .
#Text=Yes taking the sour with the sweet is a fact of life , but we should have at least 80 percent sweet when building up Vikesland .
